          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1655813240944-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the meat-free mince is browning, top, tail and chop the <strong>courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>into quarters lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Once the mince is browned, add the <strong>chopped courgette</strong> and cook for 3-4 min further or until the courgette has started to soften</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1655813245427-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1655813245427-x400.jpg",
